  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/53167ded0b094631187910cd04fa6fb6.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/53167ded0b094631187910cd04fa6fb6.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/53167ded0b094631187910cd04fa6fb6.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>YOU ARE DOG</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I AM DOG is a 2D vertical scrolling platformer where you play as DOG! Chomp, Stomp and bomb your way through dirt, stone and enemies and reach the bottom of the DEPTHS to rescue DOG’s friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/2942f9ab694be50ccb6a3f26c7a3e761.avif?t=1732035628\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/4b384454266510892e7c997f6b7e73f1.avif?t=1732035628\" width=80 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/328fb15c45a5dc5afb6b91b45b071bb1.avif?t=1732035628\" width=80 height=80 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>NEW ADVENTURE EVERY TIME!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse through procedurally generated levels featuring 4 diverse biomes filled with unique dangers and enemies! Every playthrough is a new adventure!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/8de6de8fd490ead4d5df75e165037232.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/8de6de8fd490ead4d5df75e165037232.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/8de6de8fd490ead4d5df75e165037232.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SPENDING BONES!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect bones along the way and spend them at local shops like the STOP AND GOPHE where local business entrepreneur GOPHER GODPHREY has all the best items to help you on your way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/d94d10a02454b8cb3506d64dd0ea04d2.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/d94d10a02454b8cb3506d64dd0ea04d2.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/d94d10a02454b8cb3506d64dd0ea04d2.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>COMBO METER!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stomping on every chest, mushroom, tombstone or enemy builds up your combo meter! Keep your combo going, and you’ll be rewarded with points, health, and with a high enough combo, a SUPER BONE!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/cd04c3469fd97447e0f8214aea28466e.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/cd04c3469fd97447e0f8214aea28466e.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/cd04c3469fd97447e0f8214aea28466e.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SUPER BONES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect SUPER BONES through combos or discover them in small locked-away temples! Then deposit them at the TEMPLE to upgrade DOG’s Maximum Health to help you on your journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/e123ab9dce4dc160802689d09df9e427.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/e123ab9dce4dc160802689d09df9e427.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/e123ab9dce4dc160802689d09df9e427.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HATS!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and equip DOG with ABILITY or STYLE hats! ABILITY hats that will give DOG unique abilities such as the STONE CHOMP, ½ DAMAGE or the TRIPLE JUMP. STYLE hats will double the score points to help you achieve that elusive HIGH SCORE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/7106375bf32cd8195fe6647b3c7c4cae.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/7106375bf32cd8195fe6647b3c7c4cae.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/7106375bf32cd8195fe6647b3c7c4cae.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>99 Mode!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Finishing the story unlocks 99 Mode! Play through 99 levels of randomized elements from all biomes and permanently unlock Ability Hats in your Hat Closet!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/420637042e1dd36b08427ef6fde152ab.poster.avif?t=1732035628\" width=512 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/420637042e1dd36b08427ef6fde152ab.webm?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882280/extras/420637042e1dd36b08427ef6fde152ab.mp4?t=1732035628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
